OL,3,CWorker sacked for saying 'top of the
OL,4,Cmorning to ya' wins unfair dismissal
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FMr Millward had been escorting a "red-
OL,8,Fheaded" external auditor when the
OL,9,Fremark was made and he reported his
OL,10,Fcolleague to the employer, who
OL,11,Flaunched a probe into whether the
OL,12,Fcomments amounted to racial
OL,13,Fharassment, the tribunal in Mold was
OL,14,Ftold.
OL,16,FThe claimant repeated the phrase
OL,17,Fmultiple times, with tribunal Judge
OL,18,FVincent Ryan accepting that he was
OL,19,F"effectively channelling the musical
OL,20,Fvibe".
