OL,3,CWorker sacked for saying 'top of the
OL,4,Cmorning to ya' wins unfair dismissal
OL,5,Cclaim
OL,7,FMr Davies's phrase was found by his
OL,8,Femployer to amount to harassment, but
OL,9,Fneither his clean disciplinary record
OL,10,For 27 years of employment for the firm
OL,11,Fwere taken into account, the judge
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FThe tribunal ruled that the chosen
OL,15,Finvestigator was not "appropriate",
OL,16,Fwitness statements were inconsistent
OL,17,Fand the probe was "largely based on
OL,18,Fassumptions".
OL,26,@wD@VOUwD@bO]yD@SOUzD@LO]
